Description: Provides predictive microbiology model functions and convenience
    wrappers for fitting primary growth, microbial inactivation, and cardinal
    parameter models to experimental data using nonlinear least squares.
    Includes helper functions for extracting fitted values, calculating model
    diagnostics, and comparing fitted models.
URL: https://fsqanalytics.github.io/predmicror/,
    https://github.com/fsqanalytics/predmicror
BugReports: https://github.com/fsqanalytics/predmicror/issues
